<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>1193</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qīn ài de péng yǒu qīn ài de péng yǒu, zài zhǔ lǐ yǒu yī zhēn chéng wèn hòu.
 nǐ hái hǎo ma, yuàn nǐ kuài lè yǒng jiǔ, yǒu kùn nán bù yào dī tóu.
 wǒ jīn tiān zài zhè lǐ tíng liú, yào ràng nǐ rèn shì yī wèi péng yǒu.
 tā jiù shì rén lèi de jiù zhǔ yé sū, nǐ ruò xìn tā tā bì bǎ nǐ zhěng jiù.
 nǐ ruò xìn tā tā bì bǎ nǐ zhěng jiù.</lyrics>
<title>qīn ài de péng yǒu 迦南1193</title>
</song>